User Space:
      --> Restricted Mode
      --> User level programs (applcations) -- these cannot access h/w or o/s related subsystems.

Kernel Space:
       --> Priviliged mode
       --> Kernel level code
       --> Linux kernel,subsystems and LKM
kernel level code can access memeory, peripherals, etc..


